Package: psychscore
Title: Functions for Psychometric Testing
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c( person("Joseph", "Hoyda", email = "joseph.hoyda@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: A small toolbox to help streamline the process of reverse scoring psychological tests.  Includes an interactive function for quickly performing statistical analyses on a variety of subscales.  It is designed for researchers who need to document their analysis in a script file that can be easily shared. 
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.1)
Imports:
    psych,
    plyr,
    car
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
